summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from August Mehlhorn, Jr., and Else Mehlhorn, his wife, of Seattle, Washington, to the City of Seattle, dated the 5th day of February, 1908 to Lots One (1), Two (2) and Eight (8) in Block Eight (8); Lot One (1) in Block Nine (9); Lot Three (3) and Four (4) Block Ten (10); all in Craven's Division of Green Lake Addition to the City of Seattle.
